trans-unit.source: The type of elements in the list.
trans-unit.target: 清單中項目的類型。

trans-unit.source: Represents a strongly typed list of objects that can be accessed by index.
trans-unit.target: 表示可以依照索引存取的強類型物件清單。

trans-unit.source: Provides methods to search, sort, and manipulate lists.
trans-unit.target: 提供搜尋、排序和管理清單的方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class is the generic equivalent of the <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別是泛型的對等<xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>類別。

trans-unit.source: It implements the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601> generic interface by using an array whose size is dynamically increased as required.
trans-unit.target: 它會實作<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601>需要使用陣列做為動態增加其大小的泛型介面。

trans-unit.source: You can add items to a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> by using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: 您可以將項目加入<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class uses both an equality comparer and an ordering comparer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別會使用相等比較子和排序比較子。

trans-unit.source: Methods such as <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A>, and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.Remove%2A> use an equality comparer for the list elements.
trans-unit.target: 這類方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>， <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%2A>， <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A>，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary%602.Remove%2A>為清單元素使用相等比較子。

trans-unit.source: The default equality comparer for type `T` is determined as follows.
trans-unit.target: 類型的預設相等比較子`T`決定，如下所示。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` implements the <xref:System.IEquatable%601> generic interface, then the equality comparer is the <xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%28%600%29> method of that interface; otherwise, the default equality comparer is <xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 如果型別`T`實作<xref:System.IEquatable%601>泛型介面，則相等比較子是<xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%28%600%29>方法的介面; 否則預設的相等比較子是<xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: Methods such as <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A> use an ordering comparer for the list elements.
trans-unit.target: 這類方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A>為清單元素使用排序比較子。

trans-unit.source: The default comparer for type `T` is determined as follows.
trans-unit.target: 類型的預設比較子`T`決定，如下所示。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface, then the default comparer is the <xref:System.IComparable%601.CompareTo%28%600%29> method of that interface; otherwise, if type `T` implements the nongeneric <xref:System.IComparable> interface, then the default comparer is the <xref:System.IComparable.CompareTo%28System.Object%29> method of that interface.
trans-unit.target: 如果型別`T`實作<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型介面，則預設比較子是<xref:System.IComparable%601.CompareTo%28%600%29>方法的介面; 否則如果型別`T`實作非泛型<xref:System.IComparable>介面，則預設值比較子會是<xref:System.IComparable.CompareTo%28System.Object%29>該介面的方法。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` implements neither interface, then there is no default comparer, and a comparer or comparison delegate must be provided explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 如果型別`T`實作都沒有介面，則沒有任何預設比較子，並必須明確地提供比較子或比較委派。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is not guaranteed to be sorted.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>不保證排序。

trans-unit.source: You must sort the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> before performing operations (such as <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>) that require the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> to be sorted.
trans-unit.target: 必須排序<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>之前執行的作業 (例如<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>) 需要的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>來排序。

trans-unit.source: Elements in this collection can be accessed using an integer index.
trans-unit.target: 可以使用整數索引來存取此集合中的項目。

trans-unit.source: Indexes in this collection are zero-based.
trans-unit.target: 在此集合中的索引都以零為起始。

trans-unit.source: For very large <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> objects, you can increase the maximum capacity to 2 billion elements on a 64-bit system by setting the `enabled` attribute of the configuration element to `true` in the run-time environment.
trans-unit.target: 針對大型<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>物件，您可以藉由設定增加到 64 位元系統上的 2 億元素的最大容量`enabled`屬性的組態項目`true`在執行階段環境中。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> accepts `null` as a valid value for reference types and allows duplicate elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> 接受`null`參考有效的值類型，並允許重複的項目。

trans-unit.source: For an immutable version of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class, see <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList%601>.
trans-unit.target: 不可變的新版<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別，請參閱<xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList%601>。

trans-unit.source: Performance Considerations
trans-unit.target: 效能考量

trans-unit.source: In deciding whether to use the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> or <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> class, both of which have similar functionality, remember that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class performs better in most cases and is type safe.
trans-unit.target: 決定是否要使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>或<xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>類別，這兩者都有類似的功能，請記住，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別在大部分情況下更好，和為型別安全。

trans-unit.source: If a reference type is used for type `T` of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class, the behavior of the two classes is identical.
trans-unit.target: 如果用於型別參考型別`T`的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別，這兩個類別的行為是相同。

trans-unit.source: However, if a value type is used for type `T`, you need to consider implementation and boxing issues.
trans-unit.target: 不過，如果實值型別用於型別`T`，您必須考慮實作和 boxing 問題。

trans-unit.source: If a value type is used for type `T`, the compiler generates an implementation of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class specifically for that value type.
trans-unit.target: 如果類型使用實值類型`T`，編譯器會產生的實作<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>特別針對該實值類型的類別。

trans-unit.source: That means a list element of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> object does not have to be boxed before the element can be used, and after about 500 list elements are created the memory saved not boxing list elements is greater than the memory used to generate the class implementation.
trans-unit.target: 這表示的清單項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>物件沒有可以使用的項目，再建立約 500 名 list 元素之後儲存不 boxing list 元素的記憶體是否大於用來產生類別實作的記憶體為 boxed。

trans-unit.source: Make certain the value type used for type `T` implements the <xref:System.IEquatable%601> generic interface.
trans-unit.target: 請確定用於類型的實值型別`T`實作<xref:System.IEquatable%601>泛型介面。

trans-unit.source: If not, methods such as <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> must call the <xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=nameWithType> method, which boxes the affected list element.
trans-unit.target: 如果不是，這類方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>必須呼叫<xref:System.Object.Equals%28System.Object%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法，方塊受影響的清單項目。

trans-unit.source: If the value type implements the <xref:System.IComparable> interface and you own the source code, also implement the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface to prevent the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A> methods from boxing list elements.
trans-unit.target: 如果值型別實作<xref:System.IComparable>介面，以及您擁有原始碼，也實作<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型介面，以防止<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A>boxing list 元素的方法。

trans-unit.source: If you do not own the source code, pass an <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601> object to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A> methods
trans-unit.target: 如果您並未擁有原始碼，則傳遞<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%601>物件<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A>方法

trans-unit.source: It is to your advantage to use the type-specific implementation of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class instead of using the <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> class or writing a strongly typed wrapper collection yourself.
trans-unit.target: 它會對您來說，若要使用的特定類型的實作<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別，而不是使用<xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>類別或撰寫您自己的強類型包裝函式集合。

trans-unit.source: The reason is your implementation must do what the .NET Framework does for you already, and the common language runtime can share Microsoft intermediate language code and metadata, which your implementation cannot.
trans-unit.target: 原因是您的實作必須執行.NET Framework 的用途為您，而且 common language runtime 可以共用的 Microsoft 中繼語言程式碼和中繼資料，您的實作不能。

trans-unit.source: F# Considerations
trans-unit.target: F # 的考量

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class is used infrequently in F# code.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別不常用於 F # 程式碼。

trans-unit.source: Instead, [Lists](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/83102799-f251-42e1-93ef-64232e8c5b1d), which are immutable, singly-linked lists, are typically preferred.
trans-unit.target: 相反地，[列出](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/83102799-f251-42e1-93ef-64232e8c5b1d)，這是不變且單向連結清單會通常慣用。

trans-unit.source: An F# List provides an ordered, immutable series of values, and is supported for use in functional-style development.
trans-unit.target: F # 清單提供排序、 不可變的序列的值，並支援以使用功能性方式開發。

trans-unit.source: When used from F#, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class is typically referred to by the [ResizeArray\<'T>](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ee353447.aspx) type abbreviation to avoid naming conflicts with F# Lists
trans-unit.target: 當從 F #<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別通常都有[ResizeArray\<' T >](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ee353447.aspx)類型縮寫，以避免命名衝突的 F # 清單

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to add, remove, and insert a simple business object in a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何加入、 移除和插入簡單商務物件中的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates several properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class of type string.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範數個屬性和方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字串類型的泛型類別。

trans-unit.source: (For an example of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of complex types, see the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> method.)
trans-unit.target: (如需<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的複雜型別，請參閱<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>方法。)

trans-unit.source: The default constructor is used to create a list of strings with the default capacity.
trans-unit.target: 預設建構函式用來建立字串清單的預設容量。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed and then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A> method is used to add several items.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性顯示，然後<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>方法用來加入數個項目。

trans-unit.source: The items are listed, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed again, along with the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> property, to show that the capacity has been increased as needed.
trans-unit.target: 列出項目，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性會顯示一次，連同<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性，以顯示 視需要已增加容量。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> method is used to test for the presence of an item in the list, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert a new item in the middle of the list, and the contents of the list are displayed again.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>方法用來測試是否有在清單中，項目的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用來插入新項目清單中，中間和清單的內容會顯示一次。

trans-unit.source: The default <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property (the indexer in C#) is used to retrieve an item, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A> method is used to remove the first instance of the duplicate item added earlier, and the contents are displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 預設值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A>屬性 （C# 中為索引子） 用來擷取項目，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A>方法用來移除重複的項目之前，加入第一個執行個體和內容會顯示一次。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A> method always removes the first instance it encounters.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A>方法一律會移除它遇到第一個執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method is used to reduce the capacity to match the count, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> properties are displayed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法用來減少的容量，以符合計數，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性會顯示。

trans-unit.source: If the unused capacity had been less than 10 percent of total capacity, the list would not have been resized.
trans-unit.target: 如果未使用的容量已低於 10%的總容量，清單就不調整大小。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A> method is used to remove all items from the list, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> properties are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 最後，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A>方法用來從清單中，移除所有項目和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性會顯示。

trans-unit.source: Public static (<see langword="Shared" /> in Visual Basic) members of this type are thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 公用靜態 (<see langword="Shared" />在 Visual Basic 中) 這種類型的成員都具備執行緒安全。

trans-unit.source: Any instance members are not guaranteed to be thread safe.
trans-unit.target: 不保證任何執行個體成員是安全執行緒。

trans-unit.source: It is safe to perform multiple read operations on a <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, but issues can occur if the collection is modified while it’s being read.
trans-unit.target: 您可以放心上執行多個讀取的作業<see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />，但如果在讀取時修改集合，可能會發生問題。

trans-unit.source: To ensure thread safety, lock the collection during a read or write operation.
trans-unit.target: 為確保執行緒安全，讀取過程中鎖定集合，或寫入作業。

trans-unit.source: To enable a collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要啟用以進行讀取和寫入的多重執行緒能夠存取集合，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: For collections with built-in synchronization, see the classes in the <see cref="N:System.Collections.Concurrent" /> namespace.
trans-unit.target: 對於具有內建同步處理集合，請參閱中的類別<see cref="N:System.Collections.Concurrent" />命名空間。

trans-unit.source: For an inherently thread–safe alternative, see the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList`1" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 如需原本就是安全執行緒 – 替代方法，請參閱<see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableList`1" />類別。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> class that is empty and has the default initial capacity.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 類別的新執行個體，這個執行個體為空白且具有預設的初始容量。

trans-unit.source: The capacity of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is the number of elements that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can hold.
trans-unit.target: 容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>是項目數目，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>可以保存。

trans-unit.source: As elements are added to a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, the capacity is automatically increased as required by reallocating the internal array.
trans-unit.target: 當項目加入至<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，就會自動增加容量的要求以重新配置內部的陣列。

trans-unit.source: If the size of the collection can be estimated, using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%28System.Int32%29> constructor and specifying the initial capacity eliminates the need to perform a number of resizing operations while adding elements to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 如果集合的大小可以使用來估計，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%28System.Int32%29>建構函式，並指定初始容量，就不需要執行數個調整大小作業時新增元素至<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The capacity can be decreased by calling the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method or by setting the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 藉由呼叫，您可以減少容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法或藉由設定<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性明確。

trans-unit.source: Decreasing the capacity reallocates memory and copies all the elements in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 減少容量重新配置記憶體和中的所有項目複製<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: This constructor is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 這個建構函式是 o （1） 運算。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the default constructor of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範的預設建構函式<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>泛型類別。

trans-unit.source: The default constructor creates a list with the default capacity, as demonstrated by displaying the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 預設建構函式會建立預設的容量，以清單顯示所示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性。

trans-unit.source: The example adds, inserts, and removes items, showing how the capacity changes as these methods are used.
trans-unit.target: 此範例新增、 插入，並移除項目，顯示容量的變更方式為這些方法會使用。

trans-unit.source: The collection whose elements are copied to the new list.
trans-unit.target: 將其項目複製到新清單的來源集合。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> class that contains elements copied from the specified collection and has sufficient capacity to accommodate the number of elements copied.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 類別的新執行個體，其包含從指定之集合複製的項目，且具有容納複製之項目數目的足夠容量。

trans-unit.source: The elements are copied onto the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> in the same order they are read by the enumerator of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 將元素複製到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>讀取集合的列舉值的順序相同。

trans-unit.source: This constructor is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements in `collection`.
trans-unit.target: 這個建構函式為 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是中的項目數`collection`。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%2A> constructor and various methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class that act on ranges.

trans-unit.source: An array of strings is created and passed to the constructor, populating the list with the elements of the array.
trans-unit.target: 建立並傳遞至建構函式，填入陣列的項目清單的字串陣列。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is then displayed, to show that the initial capacity is exactly what is required to hold the input elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>就顯示屬性，以顯示的初始容量是完全保留輸入項目的必要條件。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="collection" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="collection" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements that the new list can initially store.
trans-unit.target: 新清單一開始能夠儲存的項目數目。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> class that is empty and has the specified initial capacity.
trans-unit.target: 為具有指定初始容量且為空的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 類別，初始化新的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The capacity of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is the number of elements that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can hold.
trans-unit.target: 容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>是項目數目，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>可以保存。

trans-unit.source: As elements are added to a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, the capacity is automatically increased as required by reallocating the internal array.
trans-unit.target: 當項目加入至<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，就會自動增加容量的要求以重新配置內部的陣列。

trans-unit.source: If the size of the collection can be estimated, specifying the initial capacity eliminates the need to perform a number of resizing operations while adding elements to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 如果可以評估集合的大小，指定初始容量，就不需要執行數個調整大小作業時新增元素至<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The capacity can be decreased by calling the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method or by setting the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 藉由呼叫，您可以減少容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法或藉由設定<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性明確。

trans-unit.source: Decreasing the capacity reallocates memory and copies all the elements in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 減少容量重新配置記憶體和中的所有項目複製<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: This constructor is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is `capacity`.
trans-unit.target: 這個建構函式為 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是`capacity`。

trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.%23ctor%28System.Int32%29>建構函式。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings with a capacity of 4 is created, because the ultimate size of the list is known to be exactly 4.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串容量的 4 建立，因為最終大小的清單是否已知為完全 4。

trans-unit.source: The list is populated with four strings, and a read-only copy is created by using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 清單會填入四個字串，並藉由建立唯讀複本<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="capacity" /> is less than 0.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="capacity" /> 小於 0。

trans-unit.source: The object to be added to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 要加入至 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 結尾的物件。

trans-unit.source: The value can be <see langword="null" /> for reference types.
trans-unit.target: 參考類型的值可以是 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Adds an object to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 將物件加入至 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的末端。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> accepts `null` as a valid value for reference types and allows duplicate elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> 接受`null`參考有效的值類型，並允許重複的項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> already equals <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>, the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is increased by automatically reallocating the internal array, and the existing elements are copied to the new array before the new element is added.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>已等於<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>、 容量的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>增加的自動重新配置內部的陣列，並加入新項目之前現有的項目複製到新陣列。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> is less than <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>, this method is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>是小於<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>，這個方法是 o （1） 運算。

trans-unit.source: If the capacity needs to be increased to accommodate the new element, this method becomes an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 如果需要增加，以容納新項目容量，這個方法會變成 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何加入、 移除和插入簡單商務物件中的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範數個屬性和方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>泛型類別，包括<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The default constructor is used to create a list of strings with a capacity of 0.
trans-unit.target: 預設建構函式用來建立容量為 0 的字串清單。

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性隨即顯示，然後<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>方法用來加入數個項目。

trans-unit.source: The items are listed, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed again, along with the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> property, to show that the capacity has been increased as needed.
trans-unit.target: 列出項目，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性會顯示一次，連同<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性，以顯示 視需要已增加容量。

trans-unit.source: Other properties and methods are used to search for, insert, and remove elements from the list, and finally to clear the list.
trans-unit.target: 其他屬性和方法可用來搜尋、 插入和移除項目從清單中，最後再清除清單。

trans-unit.source: The collection whose elements should be added to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 集合，其項目應加入至 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的結尾。

trans-unit.source: The collection itself cannot be <see langword="null" />, but it can contain elements that are <see langword="null" />, if type <c>T</c> is a reference type.
trans-unit.target: 集合本身不可為 <see langword="null" />，但如果類型 <c>T</c> 是參考型別，則其可以包含為 <see langword="null" /> 的項目。

trans-unit.source: Adds the elements of the specified collection to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 將特定集合的項目加入至 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的結尾。

trans-unit.source: The order of the elements in the collection is preserved in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 集合中項目的順序會保留在<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: If the new <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> (the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> plus the size of the collection) will be greater than <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>, the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is increased by automatically reallocating the internal array to accommodate the new elements, and the existing elements are copied to the new array before the new elements are added.
trans-unit.target: 如果新<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>(目前<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>再加上集合的大小) 將會超過<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>、 容量的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>增加的自動重新配置以容納新項目，在內部陣列和加入新項目之前，現有的項目會複製到新陣列。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can accommodate the new elements without increasing the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements to be added.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>可容納新項目，而不會增加<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>，這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是要加入的項目數。

trans-unit.source: If the capacity needs to be increased to accommodate the new elements, this method becomes an O(*n* + *m*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements to be added and *m* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 如果需要增加，以容納新項目容量，這個方法會變成 O (*n* + *m*) 作業，其中*n*是項目數目要加入和*m*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A> method and various other methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class that act on ranges.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A>以及各種其他方法的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>處理範圍的類別。

trans-unit.source: An array of strings is created and passed to the constructor, populating the list with the elements of the array.
trans-unit.target: 建立並傳遞至建構函式，填入陣列的項目清單的字串陣列。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A> method is called, with the list as its argument.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AddRange%2A>呼叫方法時，使用當做其引數清單。

trans-unit.source: The result is that the current elements of the list are added to the end of the list, duplicating all the elements.
trans-unit.target: 結果是清單的，將目前項目加入清單中，複製所有元素的結尾。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="collection" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="collection" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns a read-only <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> wrapper for the current collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回目前集合的唯讀 <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection`1" /> 包裝函式。

trans-unit.source: An object that acts as a read-only wrapper around the current <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 此物件作為唯讀包裝函式包住目前的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />。

trans-unit.source: To prevent any modifications to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> object, expose it only through this wrapper.
trans-unit.target: 若要避免的任何修改<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>物件，請將它公開只能透過這個包裝函式。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> object does not expose methods that modify the collection.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>物件未公開修改該集合的方法。

trans-unit.source: However, if changes are made to the underlying <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> object, the read-only collection reflects those changes.
trans-unit.target: 不過，如果變更基礎<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>物件、 唯讀集合會反映這些變更。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是一種 o （1） 運算。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings with a capacity of 4 is created, because the ultimate size of the list is known to be exactly 4.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串容量的 4 建立，因為最終大小的清單是否已知為完全 4。

trans-unit.source: The list is populated with four strings, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A> method is used to get a read-only <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601> generic interface implementation that wraps the original list.
trans-unit.target: 透過四個字串，會填入此清單和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A>方法用來取得唯讀<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601>包裝原始清單的泛型介面實作。

trans-unit.source: An element of the original list is set to "Coelophysis" using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property (the indexer in C#), and the contents of the read-only list are displayed again to demonstrate that it is just a wrapper for the original list.
trans-unit.target: 將原始清單的項目設定為"Coelophysis 」 使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A>屬性 （索引子在 C# 中） 和唯讀清單的內容會顯示一次以示範它是只原始的清單包裝函式。

trans-unit.source: Uses a binary search algorithm to locate a specific element in the sorted <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> or a portion of it.
trans-unit.target: 使用二進位搜尋演算法來尋找在排序的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中或在其中一部分中的特定項目。

trans-unit.source: The object to locate.
trans-unit.target: 要尋找的物件。

trans-unit.source: The value can be <see langword="null" /> for reference types.
trans-unit.target: 參考類型的值可以是 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Searches the entire sorted <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> for an element using the default comparer and returns the zero-based index of the element.
trans-unit.target: 使用預設的比較子並傳回項目以零為起始的索引，來搜尋項目之整個排序的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of <paramref name="item" /> in the sorted <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, if <paramref name="item" /> is found; otherwise, a negative number that is the bitwise complement of the index of the next element that is larger than <paramref name="item" /> or, if there is no larger element, the bitwise complement of <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Count" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果有找到 <paramref name="item" />，則為已排序的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中 <paramref name="item" /> 之以零為起始的索引，否則便為負數，此負數為大於 <paramref name="item" /> 的下一個項目索引之位元補數，或者，如果沒有更大的項目，則為 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Count" /> 的位元補數。

trans-unit.source: This method uses the default comparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for type `T` to determine the order of list elements.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會使用預設比較子<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>類型`T`決定清單項目的順序。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface and uses that implementation, if available.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性檢查是否輸入`T`實作<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型介面，並使用該實作，如果有的話。

trans-unit.source: If not, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable> interface.
trans-unit.target: 如果沒有，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>檢查是否輸入`T`實作<xref:System.IComparable>介面。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` does not implement either interface, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 如果型別`T`未實作任何一種介面，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>會擲回<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> must already be sorted according to the comparer implementation; otherwise, the result is incorrect.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>必須先排序依據的比較子實作; 否則結果就是不正確。

trans-unit.source: Comparing `null` with any reference type is allowed and does not generate an exception when using the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface.
trans-unit.target: 比較`null`具有任何參考類型允許和不會產生例外狀況，當使用<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型介面。

trans-unit.source: When sorting, `null` is considered to be less than any other object.
trans-unit.target: 排序時，`null`會被視為小於任何其他物件。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> contains more than one element with the same value, the method returns only one of the occurrences, and it might return any one of the occurrences, not necessarily the first one.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>只會包含一個以上的項目具有相同的值，此方法會傳回其中一個相符項目，以及它可能會傳回其中一個相符項目，不一定是第一個。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> does not contain the specified value, the method returns a negative integer.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>不包含指定的值，此方法會傳回負整數。

trans-unit.source: You can apply the bitwise complement operation (~) to this negative integer to get the index of the first element that is larger than the search value.
trans-unit.target: 您可以將位元補數運算 （~） 套用至這個負整數，以取得大於搜尋值的第一個元素的索引。

trans-unit.source: When inserting the value into the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, this index should be used as the insertion point to maintain the sort order.
trans-unit.target: 插入到值時<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，這個索引應該做為插入點用來維護的排序次序。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(log *n*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements in the range.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是 O (記錄*n*) 作業，其中*n*是範圍的項目數目。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort> method overload and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method overload.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort>方法多載而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法多載。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with four strings, in no particular order.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串會建立並填入具有四個字串，不依特定順序。

trans-unit.source: The list is displayed, sorted, and displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 清單會顯示、 已排序，並且會再次顯示。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method overload is then used to search for two strings that are not in the list, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert them.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法多載然後用來搜尋兩個字串不在清單中，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用來將其插入。

trans-unit.source: The return value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method is negative in each case, because the strings are not in the list.
trans-unit.target: 傳回值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法是在每個案例中，負數的因為字串不在清單中。

trans-unit.source: Taking the bitwise complement (the ~ operator in C# and Visual C++, `Xor` -1 in Visual Basic) of this negative number produces the index of the first element in the list that is larger than the search string, and inserting at this location preserves the sort order.
trans-unit.target: 採取的位元補數 (~ 運算子，在 C# 和 Visual c + +，`Xor`在 Visual Basic 中的為-1) 的這個負的數字會產生第一個元素的清單中，在此位置是大於搜尋字串，並插入索引會保留排序順序。

trans-unit.source: The second search string is larger than any element in the list, so the insertion position is at the end of the list.

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload.

trans-unit.source: The example defines an alternative comparer for strings named DinoCompare, which implements the `IComparer<string>` (`IComparer(Of String)` in Visual Basic, `IComparer<String^>` in Visual C++) generic interface.

trans-unit.source: The comparer works as follows: First, the comparands are tested for `null`, and a null reference is treated as less than a non-null.
trans-unit.target: 比較子的運作方式如下： 第一次，針對測試比較元`null`，而且 null 的參考被視為小於一個非 null。

trans-unit.source: Second, the string lengths are compared, and the longer string is deemed to be greater.
trans-unit.target: 第二，進行比較的字串長度，以及較長的字串會視為大於。

trans-unit.source: Third, if the lengths are equal, ordinary string comparison is used.
trans-unit.target: 第三，如果長度相等，則使用一般的字串比較。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with four strings, in no particular order.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串會建立並填入具有四個字串，不依特定順序。

trans-unit.source: The list is displayed, sorted using the alternate comparer, and displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 清單會顯示，使用替代的比較子，排序並且再次顯示。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload is then used to search for several strings that are not in the list, employing the alternate comparer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert the strings.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用來插入的字串。

trans-unit.source: These two methods are located in the function named `SearchAndInsert`, along with code to take the bitwise complement (the ~ operator in C# and Visual C++, `Xor` -1 in Visual Basic) of the negative number returned by <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> and use it as an index for inserting the new string.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the total number of elements the internal data structure can hold without resizing.
trans-unit.target: 在不需要調整大小之下，取得或設定內部資料結構可以保存的項目總數。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements that the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> can contain before resizing is required.
trans-unit.target: 需要調整大小之前，<see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 可包含的項目數目。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is the number of elements that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can store before resizing is required, whereas <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> is the number of elements that are actually in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> 是的項目數，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>可以儲存需要，調整大小之前而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>是實際的項目數目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is always greater than or equal to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> 永遠是大於或等於<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> exceeds <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> while adding elements, the capacity is increased by automatically reallocating the internal array before copying the old elements and adding the new elements.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>超過<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>時加入項目，複製的舊項目並加入新項目之前，自動重新配置內部陣列增加容量。

trans-unit.source: If the capacity is significantly larger than the count and you want to reduce the memory used by the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, you can decrease capacity by calling the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method or by setting the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property explicitly to a lower value.
trans-unit.target: 如果容量更大的計數，而且您想要減少所使用的記憶體<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，您可以藉由呼叫來減少容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法或藉由設定<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性明確設為較低的值。

trans-unit.source: When the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is set explicitly, the internal array is also reallocated to accommodate the specified capacity, and all the elements are copied.
trans-unit.target: 當值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>設定明確地內部陣列也重新配置到符合指定的容量，並將複製的所有項目。

trans-unit.source: Retrieving the value of this property is an O(1) operation; setting the property is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is the new capacity.
trans-unit.target: 擷取這個屬性的值是 o （1） 運算。將屬性設定為 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是新的容量。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to check the capacity and count of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> that contains a simple business object, and illustrates using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method to remove extra capacity.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何檢查的容量和計數<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的包含簡單商務物件，並說明如何使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法，以移除額外的容量。

trans-unit.source: The following example shows the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property at several points in the life of a list.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例所示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性清單的生命週期中的數個點。

trans-unit.source: The default constructor is used to create a list of strings with a capacity of 0, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed to demonstrate this.
trans-unit.target: 預設建構函式用來建立字串清單使用的容量為 0，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>顯示屬性，以示範這點。

trans-unit.source: After the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A> method has been used to add several items, the items are listed, and then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed again, along with the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> property, to show that the capacity has been increased as needed.
trans-unit.target: 之後<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A>方法已經用來新增數個項目，項目會列出，然後<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性會顯示一次，連同<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性，以顯示 視需要已增加容量。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property is displayed again after the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method is used to reduce the capacity to match the count.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性之後，再次顯示<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法用來減少的容量，以符合計數。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A> method is used to remove all items from the list, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> properties are displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 最後，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A>方法用來從清單中，移除所有項目和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性會顯示一次。

trans-unit.source: <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Capacity" /> is set to a value that is less than <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Count" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Capacity" /> 是設定為小於 <see cref="P:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Count" /> 的值。

trans-unit.source: There is not enough memory available on the system.
trans-unit.target: 系統上沒有足夠的記憶體可用。

trans-unit.source: Removes all elements from the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 移除 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的所有項目。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> is set to 0, and references to other objects from elements of the collection are also released.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> 設定為 0，且從項目集合的其他物件的參考也會釋放。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> 維持不變。

trans-unit.source: To reset the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method or set the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property directly.
trans-unit.target: 若要重設的容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法或一組<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>直接屬性。

trans-unit.source: Decreasing the capacity reallocates memory and copies all the elements in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 減少容量重新配置記憶體和中的所有項目複製<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: Trimming an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> sets the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> to the default capacity.
trans-unit.target: 修剪空白<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>設定的容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>預設容量。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A> method and various other properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A>方法和各種其他的屬性和方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>泛型類別。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A> method is used at the end of the program, to remove all items from the list, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> properties are then displayed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A>方法用於結尾的程式，從清單中，移除所有項目和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性隨即顯示。

trans-unit.source: The object to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 要在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中尋找的物件。

trans-unit.source: The value can be <see langword="null" /> for reference types.
trans-unit.target: 參考類型的值可以是 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether an element is in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 判斷某項目是否在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="item" /> is found in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果在 <see langword="true" /> 中找到 <paramref name="item" />，則為 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: This method determines equality by using the default equality comparer, as defined by the object's implementation of the <xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method for `T` (the type of values in the list).
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會判斷所使用的預設相等比較子，等號比較的物件的實作所定義<xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法`T`（清單中的值類型）。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行線性搜尋;因此，這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> methods on a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> that contains a simple business object that implements <xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，其中包含實作簡單商務物件<xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example contains a list of complex objects of type `Cube`.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例包含型別之複雜物件一份`Cube`。

trans-unit.source: The `Cube` class implements the <xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method so that two cubes are considered equal if their dimensions are the same.
trans-unit.target: `Cube`類別會實作<xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法使兩個 cube 會被視為相等，如果是相同的維度。

trans-unit.source: In this example, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> method returns `true`, because a cube that has the specified dimensions is already in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 在此範例中，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>方法會傳回`true`，因為已指定的維度的 cube 已經在集合中。

trans-unit.source: The type of the elements of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 目標陣列項目的類型。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Converter`2" /> delegate that converts each element from one type to another type.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Converter`2" /> 委派，可將某一個類型的每一個項目轉換成另一個類型。

trans-unit.source: Converts the elements in the current <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> to another type, and returns a list containing the converted elements.
trans-unit.target: 將目前 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的項目轉換成另一個類型，並傳回包含轉換過的項目清單。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> of the target type containing the converted elements from the current <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 目標類型的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />，包含從目前 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中轉換過的項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Converter%602> is a delegate to a method that converts an object to the target type.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Converter%602>是將物件轉換成目標型別方法委派。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Converter%602> delegate, and the converted elements are saved in the new <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 目前的項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>分別傳遞至<xref:System.Converter%602>委派，而且已轉換的項目會儲存在新<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 目前<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>維持不變。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example defines a method named `PointFToPoint` that converts a <xref:System.Drawing.PointF> structure to a <xref:System.Drawing.Point> structure.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會定義方法，名為`PointFToPoint`將轉換<xref:System.Drawing.PointF>結構以<xref:System.Drawing.Point>結構。

trans-unit.source: The example then creates a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of <xref:System.Drawing.PointF> structures, creates a `Converter\<PointF, Point>` delegate (`Converter(Of PointF, Point)` in Visual Basic) to represent the `PointFToPoint` method, and passes the delegate to the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.ConvertAll%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 這個範例會建立<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的<xref:System.Drawing.PointF>結構、 建立`Converter\<PointF, Point>`委派 (`Converter(Of PointF, Point)`在 Visual Basic 中) 來代表`PointFToPoint`方法，並傳遞至委派<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.ConvertAll%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.ConvertAll%2A> method passes each element of the input list to the `PointFToPoint` method and puts the converted elements into a new list of <xref:System.Drawing.Point> structures.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.ConvertAll%2A>方法會將傳遞的輸入清單的每個項目`PointFToPoint`方法並將已轉換的項目放入新的清單<xref:System.Drawing.Point>結構。

trans-unit.source: Both lists are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 這兩份清單會顯示。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="converter" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="converter" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: Copies the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> or a portion of it to an array.
trans-unit.target: 將 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 或其中一部分複製到陣列。

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 一維 <see cref="T:System.Array" />，是從 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 複製過來之項目的目的端。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Array" /> 必須有以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> to a compatible one-dimensional array, starting at the beginning of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 從目標陣列的開頭開始，將整個 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 複製到相容的一維陣列。

trans-unit.source: This method uses <xref:System.Array.Copy%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to copy the elements.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會使用<xref:System.Array.Copy%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>複製項目。

trans-unit.source: The elements are copied to the <xref:System.Array> in the same order in which the enumerator iterates through the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 將元素複製到<xref:System.Array>以相同的順序，以列舉值逐一<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates all three overloads of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範的所有三個多載<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with 5 strings.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串會建立並填入具有 5 個字串。

trans-unit.source: An empty string array of 15 elements is created, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%29> method overload is used to copy all the elements of the list to the array beginning at the first element of the array.
trans-unit.target: 建立空白的字串陣列的 15 項目，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%29>方法多載用來將清單中的所有元素都複製到開始於陣列的第一個元素的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to copy all the elements of the list to the array beginning at array index 6 (leaving index 5 empty).
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法多載用來複製所有的項目清單的陣列索引 6 開始的陣列 （讓索引 5 空白）。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28System.Int32%2C%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to copy 3 elements from the list, beginning with index 2, to the array beginning at array index 12 (leaving index 11 empty).
trans-unit.target: 最後，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28System.Int32%2C%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法多載用來複製 3 個元素，從清單中，從索引 2 開始，到開始於陣列的陣列索引 12 （讓索引 11 空白）。

trans-unit.source: The contents of the array are then displayed.
trans-unit.target: 陣列的內容隨即顯示。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> is greater than the number of elements that the destination <paramref name="array" /> can contain.
trans-unit.target: 來源 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的項目數大於目的 <paramref name="array" /> 可包含的項目數。

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 一維 <see cref="T:System.Array" />，是從 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 複製過來之項目的目的端。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Array" /> 必須有以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>array</c> 中以零起始的索引，複製作業從此處開始。

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> to a compatible one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 從目標陣列的指定索引處開始，將整個 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 複製到相容的一維陣列中。

trans-unit.source: This method uses <xref:System.Array.Copy%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to copy the elements.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會使用<xref:System.Array.Copy%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>複製項目。

trans-unit.source: The elements are copied to the <xref:System.Array> in the same order in which the enumerator iterates through the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 將元素複製到<xref:System.Array>以相同的順序，以列舉值逐一<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with 5 strings.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串會建立並填入具有 5 個字串。

trans-unit.source: An empty string array of 15 elements is created, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%29> method overload is used to copy all the elements of the list to the array beginning at the first element of the array.
trans-unit.target: 建立空白的字串陣列的 15 項目，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%29>方法多載用來將清單中的所有元素都複製到開始於陣列的第一個元素的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to copy all the elements of the list to the array beginning at array index 6 (leaving index 5 empty).

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28System.Int32%2C%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to copy 3 elements from the list, beginning with index 2, to the array beginning at array index 12 (leaving index 11 empty).
trans-unit.target: 最後，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.CopyTo%28System.Int32%2C%600%5B%5D%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法多載用來複製 3 個元素，從清單中，從索引 2 開始，到開始於陣列的陣列索引 12 （讓索引 11 空白）。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is the number of elements that the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can store before resizing is required.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> 是的項目數，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>需要調整大小之前，可以儲存。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> is the number of elements that are actually in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> 是實際的項目數目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> is always greater than or equal to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> 永遠是大於或等於<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> exceeds <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> while adding elements, the capacity is increased by automatically reallocating the internal array before copying the old elements and adding the new elements.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>超過<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>時加入項目，複製的舊項目並加入新項目之前，自動重新配置內部陣列增加容量。

trans-unit.source: Retrieving the value of this property is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 擷取這個屬性的值是一種 O(1) 運算。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to check the capacity and count of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> that contains a simple business object, and illustrates using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method to remove extra capacity.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何檢查的容量和計數<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的包含簡單商務物件，並說明如何使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法，以移除額外的容量。

trans-unit.source: The following example shows the value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> property at various points in the life of a list.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例顯示的值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>生命週期的清單中的各個點上的屬性。

trans-unit.source: After the list has been created and populated and its elements displayed, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> properties are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 已建立並填入清單並顯示其項目之後,<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性會顯示。

trans-unit.source: These properties are displayed again after the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method has been called, and again after the contents of the list are cleared.
trans-unit.target: 這些屬性會顯示之後，再次<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法已被呼叫，和清單的內容之後，再次清除。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> delegate that defines the conditions of the elements to search for.
trans-unit.target: 定義要搜尋項目之條件的 <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> 委派。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> contains elements that match the conditions defined by the specified predicate.
trans-unit.target: 判斷 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 是否包含符合指定之述詞所定義之條件的項目。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> contains one or more elements that match the conditions defined by the specified predicate; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 包含的一或多個項目符合指定之述詞所定義的條件，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Predicate%601> is a delegate to a method that returns `true` if the object passed to it matches the conditions defined in the delegate.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Predicate%601>委派的方法會傳回以`true`傳送至的物件是否符合在委派中定義的條件。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Predicate%601> delegate, and processing is stopped when a match is found.
trans-unit.target: 目前的項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>分別傳遞至<xref:System.Predicate%601>的委派，以及處理會停止時找到相符項目。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行線性搜尋;因此，這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> methods on a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> that contains a simple business object that implements <xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Contains%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，其中包含實作簡單商務物件<xref:System.IEquatable%601.Equals%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> method and several other methods that use the <xref:System.Predicate%601> generic delegate.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>以及數個使用其他方法<xref:System.Predicate%601>泛型委派。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, containing 8 dinosaur names, two of which (at positions 1 and 5) end with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字串的建立，其中包含 8 恐龍名稱，兩個 （在位置 1 和 5） 」 saurus 」 以結束。

trans-unit.source: The example also defines a search predicate method named `EndsWithSaurus`, which accepts a string parameter and returns a Boolean value indicating whether the input string ends in "saurus".
trans-unit.target: 此範例也會定義名為的搜尋述詞方法`EndsWithSaurus`、 可接受字串參數和傳回布林值，指出是否"saurus"輸入的字串結尾。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLast%2A>, and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindAll%2A> methods are used to search the list with the search predicate method, and then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A> method is used to remove all entries ending with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A>， <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLast%2A>，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindAll%2A>方法會用於搜尋與搜尋述詞方法的清單，然後<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A>方法用來移除所有項目結尾"saurus"。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: 最後，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>方法呼叫。

trans-unit.source: It traverses the list from the beginning, passing each element in turn to the `EndsWithSaurus` method.
trans-unit.target: 周遊清單開頭，接著為傳遞每個項目從`EndsWithSaurus`方法。

trans-unit.source: The search stops and the method returns `true` if the `EndsWithSaurus` method returns `true` for any element.
trans-unit.target: 搜尋時，會停止，則方法會傳回`true`如果`EndsWithSaurus`方法會傳回`true`的任何項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> method returns `false` because all such elements have been removed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>方法會傳回`false`由於所有這類項目已經移除。

trans-unit.source: In C# and Visual Basic, it is not necessary to create the `Predicate<string>` delegate (`Predicate(Of String)` in Visual Basic) explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 在 C# 和 Visual Basic 中，就不需要建立`Predicate<string>`委派 (`Predicate(Of String)`在 Visual Basic 中) 明確。

trans-unit.source: These languages infer the correct delegate from context and create it automatically.
trans-unit.target: 這些語言推斷正確的委派，從內容，並自動建立。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="match" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="match" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> delegate that defines the conditions of the element to search for.
trans-unit.target: 定義要搜尋項目之條件的 <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> 委派。

trans-unit.source: Searches for an element that matches the conditions defined by the specified predicate, and returns the first occurrence within the entire <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 搜尋符合指定之述詞所定義的條件之項目，並傳回整個 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 內第一個相符的項目。

trans-unit.source: The first element that matches the conditions defined by the specified predicate, if found; otherwise, the default value for type <paramref name="T" />.
trans-unit.target: 第一個符合指定之述詞所定義的條件之項目 (如有找到)，否則為類型 <paramref name="T" /> 的預設值。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Predicate%601> is a delegate to a method that returns `true` if the object passed to it matches the conditions defined in the delegate.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Predicate%601>委派的方法會傳回以`true`傳送至的物件是否符合在委派中定義的條件。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Predicate%601> delegate, moving forward in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, starting with the first element and ending with the last element.
trans-unit.target: 目前的項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>分別傳遞至<xref:System.Predicate%601>委派，在中向前移動<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>、 第一個元素開始和結尾最後一個項目。

trans-unit.source: Processing is stopped when a match is found.
trans-unit.target: 找到相符項目時，會停止處理。

trans-unit.source: When searching a list containing value types, make sure the default value for the type does not satisfy the search predicate.
trans-unit.target: 搜尋時包含實值類型的清單，請確定類型的預設值不符合搜尋述詞。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, there is no way to distinguish between a default value indicating that no match was found and a list element that happens to have the default value for the type.
trans-unit.target: 否則，就沒有預設值，指出沒有相符項目找不到與那麼類型的預設值的清單項目之間進行區別。

trans-unit.source: If the default value satisfies the search predicate, use the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindIndex%2A> method instead.
trans-unit.target: 預設值符合此搜尋述詞，如果使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindIndex%2A>方法改為。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行線性搜尋;因此，這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A> method on a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> that contains a simple complex object.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A>方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，其中包含簡單的複雜物件。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the find methods for the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範尋找方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別。

trans-unit.source: The example for the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class contains `book` objects, of class `Book`, using the data from the [Sample XML File: Books (LINQ to XML)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/94252daf-6097-4625-afc2-0eb778958d4f).
trans-unit.target: 如範例<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別包含`book`類別的物件`Book`，使用中的資料[範例 XML 檔： 書籍 (LINQ to XML)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/94252daf-6097-4625-afc2-0eb778958d4f)。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Predicate%601> is a delegate to a method that returns `true` if the object passed to it matches the conditions defined in the delegate.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Predicate%601>委派的方法會傳回以`true`傳送至的物件是否符合在委派中定義的條件。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Predicate%601> delegate, moving backward in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, starting with the last element and ending with the first element.
trans-unit.target: 目前的項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>分別傳遞至<xref:System.Predicate%601>委派，在中向後移動<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>、 最後一個元素開始和結束的第一個元素。

trans-unit.source: Processing is stopped when a match is found.
trans-unit.target: 找到相符項目時，會停止處理。

trans-unit.source: When searching a list containing value types, make sure the default value for the type does not satisfy the search predicate.
trans-unit.target: 搜尋時包含實值類型的清單，請確定類型的預設值不符合搜尋述詞。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, there is no way to distinguish between a default value indicating that no match was found and a list element that happens to have the default value for the type.
trans-unit.target: 否則，就沒有預設值，指出沒有相符項目找不到與那麼類型的預設值的清單項目之間進行區別。

trans-unit.source: If the default value satisfies the search predicate, use the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLastIndex%2A> method instead.
trans-unit.target: 預設值符合此搜尋述詞，如果使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLastIndex%2A>方法改為。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行線性搜尋;因此，這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Action%601> is a delegate to a method that performs an action on the object passed to it.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Action%601>物件執行的動作方法的委派傳遞給它。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Action%601> delegate.
trans-unit.target: 目前的項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>分別傳遞至<xref:System.Action%601>委派。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: Modifying the underlying collection in the body of the <xref:System.Action%601> delegate is not supported and causes undefined behavior.
trans-unit.target: 修改基礎集合中的主體<xref:System.Action%601>委派不支援，而且會導致未定義的行為。
