trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: 傳回在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中逐一查看的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Enumerator" /> for the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1.Enumerator" /> 的 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of the enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + +`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 會隱藏列舉值的複雜度。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 此位置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>未定義屬性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，您必須呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法，以將列舉值前進到第一個項目，再讀取的值集合的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> property returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>屬性會傳回相同的物件直到<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>呼叫。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 您不能再次將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Enumerator.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個項目；您必須建立新的列舉值執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果對集合進行變更，例如加入、修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，且其行為未定義。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式沒有集合的獨佔存取權，因此，列舉集合內容本質上並不是安全的執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: To guarantee thread safety during enumeration, you can lock the collection during the entire enumeration.
trans-unit.target: 若要確保列舉期間的執行緒安全性，您可以在整個列舉期間鎖定集合。

trans-unit.source: To allow the collection to be accessed by multiple threads for reading and writing, you must implement your own synchronization.
trans-unit.target: 若要讓多重執行緒能夠存取集合以便進行讀取和寫入，您必須實作自己的同步處理。

trans-unit.source: Default implementations of collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace are not synchronized.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic?displayProperty=nameWithType> 命名空間中集合的預設實作未同步處理。

trans-unit.source: A shallow copy of a collection of reference types, or a subset of that collection, contains only the references to the elements of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 參考類型的集合或子集該集合的淺層複本只包含參考的集合項目。

trans-unit.source: The references in the new list point to the same objects as the references in the original list.
trans-unit.target: 新的清單中的參考會指向原始的清單中的參考相同的物件。

trans-unit.source: A shallow copy of a collection of value types, or a subset of that collection, contains the elements of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 淺層複本實值類型的集合或子集該集合，包含集合的元素。

trans-unit.source: However, if the elements of the collection contain references to other objects, those objects are not copied.
trans-unit.target: 不過，如果集合的元素會包含其他物件的參考，不會複製這些物件。

trans-unit.source: The references in the elements of the new collection point to the same objects as the references in the elements of the original collection.
trans-unit.target: 新集合的項目中參考指向原始集合的項目中參考相同的物件。

trans-unit.source: In contrast, a deep copy of a collection copies the elements and everything directly or indirectly referenced by the elements.
trans-unit.target: 相反地，項目複製集合的深層複本，並直接或間接參考之項目，所有項目。

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified object and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the range of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> that starts at the specified index and contains the specified number of elements.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the first occurrence of <paramref name="item" /> within the range of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> that starts at <paramref name="index" /> and contains <paramref name="count" /> number of elements, if found; otherwise, –1.
trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中從 <paramref name="index" /> 開始且包含 <paramref name="count" /> 個項目的範圍內，第一次出現 <paramref name="item" /> 之以零為起始的索引，如未找到則為 -1。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> is searched forward starting at `index` and ending at `index` plus `count` minus 1, if `count` is greater than 0.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>開始向前搜尋`index`結束為`index`加上`count`減 1，如果`count`大於 0。

trans-unit.source: This method determines equality using the default equality comparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.EqualityComparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for `T`, the type of values in the list.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會決定使用的預設相等比較子的等號比較<xref:System.Collections.Generic.EqualityComparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>如`T`，清單中值的類型。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is `count`.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行線性搜尋;因此，這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是`count`。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates all three overloads of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範的所有三個多載<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, with one entry that appears twice, at index location 0 and index location 5.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串將建立一個會出現兩次，在索引位置 0 和 5 的索引位置的項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%28%600%29> method overload searches the list from the beginning, and finds the first occurrence of the string.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%28%600%29>方法多載會開始時，從清單中搜尋和尋找字串的第一個項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search the list beginning with index location 3 and continuing to the end of the list, and finds the second occurrence of the string.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法多載用於搜尋的索引位置 3 開頭的清單和清單的結尾繼續，並尋找字串的第二個項目。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search a range of two entries, beginning at index location two; it returns –1 because there are no instances of the search string in that range.
trans-unit.target: 最後，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.IndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法多載用來搜尋指定範圍的開頭的索引位置 2 的兩個項目; 它會傳回 – 1，因為沒有在該範圍內的搜尋字串的執行個體。

trans-unit.target: 如果`index`等於<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>，`item`加入至結尾<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: After the list has been created and populated using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Add%2A> method, an element is retrieved and displayed using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property.

trans-unit.source: (For an example that uses the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property to set the value of a list element, see <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.AsReadOnly%2A>.)

trans-unit.source: Visual Basic, C#, and C++ all have syntax for accessing the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Item%2A> property without using its name.

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates all three overloads of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範的所有三個多載<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, with one entry that appears twice, at index location 0 and index location 5.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串將建立一個會出現兩次，在索引位置 0 和 5 的索引位置的項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%29> method overload searches the entire list from the end, and finds the second occurrence of the string.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%29>方法多載會整個結束時，從清單中搜尋和尋找字串的第二個項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search the list backward beginning with index location 3 and continuing to the beginning of the list, so it finds the first occurrence of the string in the list.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法多載用來搜尋回溯開頭的索引位置為 3，並繼續清單的開頭，讓它在清單中尋找第一個字串的清單。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search a range of four entries, beginning at index location 4 and extending backward (that is, it searches the items at locations 4, 3, 2, and 1); this search returns –1 because there are no instances of the search string in that range.
trans-unit.target: 最後，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法多載用於範圍之四個項目，索引位置 4 開始，並擴充向後搜尋 （也就是說，它會搜尋的項目在位置 4、 3、 2 和 1）; 此搜尋會傳回 – 1，因為沒有搜尋的執行個體在該範圍內的字串。

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified object and returns the zero-based index of the last occurrence within the range of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> that extends from the first element to the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中從第一個項目開始到指定的索引這段範圍內，搜尋指定的物件最後一次出現的位置，並傳回其索引值 (索引以零為起始)。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the last occurrence of <paramref name="item" /> within the range of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> that extends from the first element to <paramref name="index" />, if found; otherwise, –1.
trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中從第一個項目開始到 <paramref name="index" /> 這段範圍內，如果有找到指定的 <paramref name="item" /> 最後一次出現的位置，則為該位置以零為起始的索引，如未找到則為 -1。

trans-unit.target: 這個方法會決定使用的預設相等比較子的等號比較<xref:System.Collections.Generic.EqualityComparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>如`T`，清單中值的類型。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, this method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is the number of elements from the beginning of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> to `index`.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行線性搜尋;因此，這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是從開頭的項目數<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>至`index`。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates all three overloads of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範的所有三個多載<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, with one entry that appears twice, at index location 0 and index location 5.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串將建立一個會出現兩次，在索引位置 0 和 5 的索引位置的項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%29> method overload searches the entire list from the end, and finds the second occurrence of the string.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%29>方法多載會整個結束時，從清單中搜尋和尋找字串的第二個項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search the list backward beginning with index location 3 and continuing to the beginning of the list, so it finds the first occurrence of the string in the list.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法多載用來搜尋回溯開頭的索引位置為 3，並繼續清單的開頭，讓它在清單中尋找第一個字串的清單。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29> method overload is used to search a range of four entries, beginning at index location 4 and extending backward (that is, it searches the items at locations 4, 3, 2, and 1); this search returns –1 because there are no instances of the search string in that range.
trans-unit.target: 最後，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.LastIndexOf%28%600%2CSystem.Int32%2CSystem.Int32%29>方法多載用於範圍之四個項目，索引位置 4 開始，並擴充向後搜尋 （也就是說，它會搜尋的項目在位置 4、 3、 2 和 1）; 此搜尋會傳回 – 1，因為沒有搜尋的執行個體在該範圍內的字串。

trans-unit.source: Several properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> generic class are used to add, insert, and search the list.
trans-unit.target: 數個屬性和方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>泛型類別可用來加入、 插入及搜尋清單。

trans-unit.source: After these operations, the list contains a duplicate.
trans-unit.target: 這些作業之後，此清單包含重複項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A> method is used to remove the first instance of the duplicate item, and the contents are displayed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A>方法用來移除重複的項目，第一個執行個體和內容會顯示。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A> method always removes the first instance it encounters.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Remove%2A>方法一律會移除它遇到第一個執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> delegate that defines the conditions of the elements to remove.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> 委派，定義要移除項目的條件。

trans-unit.source: Removes all the elements that match the conditions defined by the specified predicate.
trans-unit.target: 移除符合指定的述詞所定義之條件的所有項目。

trans-unit.source: The number of elements removed from the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> .
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中已移除的項目數。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Predicate%601> is a delegate to a method that returns `true` if the object passed to it matches the conditions defined in the delegate.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Predicate%601>委派的方法會傳回以`true`傳送至的物件是否符合在委派中定義的條件。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Predicate%601> delegate, and the elements that match the conditions are removed from the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>.
trans-unit.target: 目前的項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>分別傳遞至<xref:System.Predicate%601>委派，而且符合之條件的項目會從<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A> method and several other methods that use the <xref:System.Predicate%601> generic delegate.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A>以及數個使用其他方法<xref:System.Predicate%601>泛型委派。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, containing 8 dinosaur names, two of which (at positions 1 and 5) end with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字串的建立，其中包含 8 恐龍名稱，兩個 （在位置 1 和 5） 」 saurus 」 以結束。

trans-unit.source: The example also defines a search predicate method named `EndsWithSaurus`, which accepts a string parameter and returns a Boolean value indicating whether the input string ends in "saurus".
trans-unit.target: 此範例也會定義名為的搜尋述詞方法`EndsWithSaurus`、 可接受字串參數和傳回布林值，指出是否"saurus"輸入的字串結尾。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLast%2A>, and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindAll%2A> methods are used to search the list with the search predicate method.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Find%2A>， <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindLast%2A>，和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.FindAll%2A>方法可用來在清單中搜尋的搜尋述詞的方法。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A> method is used to remove all entries ending with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAll%2A>方法用來移除所有項目結尾"saurus"。

trans-unit.source: It traverses the list from the beginning, passing each element in turn to the `EndsWithSaurus` method.
trans-unit.target: 周遊清單開頭，接著為傳遞每個項目從`EndsWithSaurus`方法。

trans-unit.source: The element is removed if the `EndsWithSaurus` method returns `true`.
trans-unit.target: 如果移除元素`EndsWithSaurus`方法會傳回`true`。

trans-unit.source: In C# and Visual Basic, it is not necessary to create the `Predicate<string>` delegate (`Predicate(Of String)` in Visual Basic) explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 在 C# 和 Visual Basic 中，就不需要建立`Predicate<string>`委派 (`Predicate(Of String)`在 Visual Basic 中) 明確。

trans-unit.source: These languages infer the correct delegate from context, and create it automatically.
trans-unit.target: 這些語言推斷正確的委派，從內容，並自動建立。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A> method verifies that there are no strings in the list that end with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: 最後，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Exists%2A>方法會驗證不是否在清單中以"saurus"結尾的任何字串。

trans-unit.source: When you call <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAt%2A> to remove an item, the remaining items in the list are renumbered to replace the removed item.
trans-unit.target: 當您呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.RemoveAt%2A>移除項目，在清單中其餘的項目會重新編號來取代已移除的項目。

trans-unit.source: For example, if you remove the item at index 3, the item at index 4 is moved to the 3 position.
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果您移除位於索引 3 的項目時，索引 4 的項目移到 3 的位置。

trans-unit.source: In addition, the number of items in the list (as represented by the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> property) is reduced by 1.
trans-unit.target: 此外，在清單中的項目數 (所表示的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性) 會減 1。

trans-unit.source: Sorts the elements in the entire <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> using the default comparer.
trans-unit.target: 使用預設的比較子來排序在整個 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的項目。

trans-unit.source: This method uses the default comparer <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for type `T` to determine the order of list elements.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會使用預設比較子<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>類型`T`決定清單項目的順序。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable%601> generic interface and uses that implementation, if available.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性檢查是否輸入`T`實作<xref:System.IComparable%601>泛型介面，並使用該實作，如果有的話。

trans-unit.source: If not, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> checks whether type `T` implements the <xref:System.IComparable> interface.
trans-unit.target: 如果沒有，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>檢查是否輸入`T`實作<xref:System.IComparable>介面。

trans-unit.source: If type `T` does not implement either interface, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> throws an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: 如果型別`T`未實作任何一種介面，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.Comparer%601.Default%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>會擲回<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。

trans-unit.source: This method uses the <xref:System.Array.Sort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method, which applies the introspective sort as follows:
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會使用<xref:System.Array.Sort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>方法，適用於內省式排序，如下所示：

trans-unit.source: If the partition size is fewer than 16 elements, it uses an insertion sort algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 如果磁碟分割大小是 16 個元素，它會使用插入排序演算法。

trans-unit.source: If the number of partitions exceeds 2 log *n*, where *n* is the range of the input array, it uses a Heapsort algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 如果資料分割數目超過 2 記錄*n*，其中*n*為範圍之輸入的陣列，它會使用 Heapsort 演算法。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it uses a Quicksort algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 否則，它會使用快速排序演算法。

trans-unit.source: This implementation performs an unstable sort; that is, if two elements are equal, their order might not be preserved.
trans-unit.target: 此實作會執行不穩定的排序。也就是說，如果兩個項目相同，可能不會保留它們的順序。

trans-unit.source: In contrast, a stable sort preserves the order of elements that are equal.
trans-unit.target: 相較之下，穩定的排序會保留相同的項目的順序。

trans-unit.source: On average, this method is an O(*n* log *n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>; in the worst case it is an O(*n*<sup>2</sup>) operation.
trans-unit.target: 平均而言，這個方法是 O (*n*記錄*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>; 最壞的情況下為 O (*n* <sup>2</sup>) 作業。

trans-unit.source: The following example adds some names to a `List<String>` object, displays the list in unsorted order, calls the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A> method, and then displays the sorted list.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會將一些名稱來`List<String>`物件，會顯示未排序的順序，清單便會呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%2A>方法，然後顯示 已排序的清單。

trans-unit.source: The following code demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Comparison%7B%600%7D%29> method overloads on a simple business object.
trans-unit.target: 下列程式碼示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Comparison%7B%600%7D%29>簡單商務物件上的方法多載。

trans-unit.source: Calling the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort> method results in the use of the default comparer for the Part type, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Comparison%7B%600%7D%29> method is implemented by using an anonymous method.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort>方法會產生做為部分類型，使用預設比較子和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Comparison%7B%600%7D%29>使用匿名方法實作方法。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort> method overload and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method overload.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort>方法多載而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法多載。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with four strings, in no particular order.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串會建立並填入具有四個字串，不依特定順序。

trans-unit.source: The list is displayed, sorted, and displayed again.
trans-unit.target: 清單會顯示、 已排序，並且會再次顯示。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29> method overload is then used to search for two strings that are not in the list, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert them.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%29>方法多載然後用來搜尋兩個字串不在清單中，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用來將其插入。

trans-unit.source: The return value of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A> method is negative in each case, because the strings are not in the list.
trans-unit.target: 傳回值<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%2A>方法是在每個案例中，負數的因為字串不在清單中。

trans-unit.source: Taking the bitwise complement (the ~ operator in C# and Visual C++, `Xor` -1 in Visual Basic) of this negative number produces the index of the first element in the list that is larger than the search string, and inserting at this location preserves the sort order.
trans-unit.target: 採取的位元補數 (~ 運算子，在 C# 和 Visual c + +，`Xor`在 Visual Basic 中的為-1) 的這個負的數字會產生第一個元素的清單中，在此位置是大於搜尋字串，並插入索引會保留排序順序。

trans-unit.source: The second search string is larger than any element in the list, so the insertion position is at the end of the list.
trans-unit.target: 第二個搜尋字串大於任何項目在清單中，所以插入位置在清單的結尾。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Sort%28System.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法多載而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>方法多載。

trans-unit.source: The example defines an alternative comparer for strings named DinoCompare, which implements the `IComparer<string>` (`IComparer(Of String)` in Visual Basic, `IComparer<String^>` in Visual C++) generic interface.
trans-unit.target: 此範例會定義名為 DinoCompare，實作字串的替代比較子`IComparer<string>`(`IComparer(Of String)`在 Visual Basic 中`IComparer<String^>`Visual c + +) 泛型介面。

trans-unit.source: The comparer works as follows: First, the comparands are tested for `null`, and a null reference is treated as less than a non-null.
trans-unit.target: 比較子的運作方式如下： 第一次，針對測試比較元`null`，而且 null 的參考被視為小於一個非 null。

trans-unit.source: Second, the string lengths are compared, and the longer string is deemed to be greater.
trans-unit.target: 第二，進行比較的字串長度，以及較長的字串會視為大於。

trans-unit.source: Third, if the lengths are equal, ordinary string comparison is used.
trans-unit.target: 第三，如果長度相等，則使用一般的字串比較。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with four strings, in no particular order.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串會建立並填入具有四個字串，不依特定順序。

trans-unit.source: The list is displayed, sorted using the alternate comparer, and displayed again.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> method overload is then used to search for several strings that are not in the list, employing the alternate comparer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A> method is used to insert the strings.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Insert%2A>方法用來插入的字串。

trans-unit.source: These two methods are located in the function named `SearchAndInsert`, along with code to take the bitwise complement (the ~ operator in C# and Visual C++, `Xor` -1 in Visual Basic) of the negative number returned by <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29> and use it as an index for inserting the new string.
trans-unit.target: 這兩種方法位於名為函式`SearchAndInsert`，以及程式碼，要採取的位元補數 (~ 運算子，在 C# 和 Visual c + +，`Xor`在 Visual Basic 中的為-1) 所傳回的負數的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.BinarySearch%28%600%2CSystem.Collections.Generic.IComparer%7B%600%7D%29>並使用它做為索引插入新的字串。

trans-unit.source: If `comparison` is provided, the elements of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are sorted using the method represented by the delegate.
trans-unit.target: 如果`comparison`提供的項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>排序使用委派所表示的方法。

trans-unit.source: If `comparison` is `null`, an <xref:System.ArgumentNullException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: 如果`comparison`是`null`、<xref:System.ArgumentNullException>就會擲回。

trans-unit.source: This method uses <xref:System.Array.Sort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, which applies the introspective sort as follows:
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會使用<xref:System.Array.Sort%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>，這會套用內省式排序，如下所示：

trans-unit.source: If the partition size is fewer than 16 elements, it uses an insertion sort algorithm
trans-unit.target: 如果磁碟分割大小是 16 個元素，它會使用插入排序演算法

trans-unit.source: If the number of partitions exceeds 2 log *n*, where *n* is the range of the input array, it uses a [Heapsort](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heapsort) algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 如果資料分割數目超過 2 記錄*n*，其中*n*為範圍之輸入的陣列，它會使用[Heapsort](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heapsort)演算法。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it uses a Quicksort algorithm.
trans-unit.target: 否則，它會使用快速排序演算法。

trans-unit.source: This implementation performs an unstable sort; that is, if two elements are equal, their order might not be preserved.
trans-unit.target: 此實作會執行不穩定的排序。也就是說，如果兩個項目相同，可能不會保留它們的順序。

trans-unit.source: In contrast, a stable sort preserves the order of elements that are equal.
trans-unit.target: 相較之下，穩定的排序會保留相同的項目的順序。

trans-unit.source: On average, this method is an O(*n* log *n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>; in the worst case it is an O(*n*<sup>2</sup>) operation.
trans-unit.target: 平均而言，這個方法是 O (*n*記錄*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>; 最壞的情況下為 O (*n* <sup>2</sup>) 作業。

trans-unit.source: The example defines an alternative comparison method for strings, named `CompareDinosByLength`.

trans-unit.source: This method works as follows: First, the comparands are tested for `null`, and a null reference is treated as less than a non-null.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法的運作方式如下： 第一次，針對測試比較元`null`，而且 null 的參考被視為小於一個非 null。

trans-unit.target: 第二，進行比較的字串長度，以及較長的字串會視為大於。

trans-unit.source: Third, if the lengths are equal, ordinary string comparison is used.
trans-unit.target: 第三，如果長度相等，則使用一般的字串比較。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created and populated with four strings, in no particular order.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的字串會建立並填入具有四個字串，不依特定順序。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，指出 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> 是否唯讀。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" /> is read-only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see langword="true" /> 是唯讀，則為 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection`1" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: In the default implementation of <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, this property always returns <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的預設實作中，這個屬性一律會傳回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: A collection that is read-only does not allow the addition, removal, or modification of elements after the collection is created.
trans-unit.target: 唯讀的集合不允許在集合建立後增加、移除或修改項目。

trans-unit.source: A collection that is read-only is simply a collection with a wrapper that prevents modifying the collection; therefore, if changes are made to the underlying collection, the read-only collection reflects those changes.
trans-unit.target: 是唯讀的集合是唯讀的集合只具有可防止修改集合的包裝函式因此，如果基礎集合進行變更，唯讀的集合會反映這些變更。

trans-unit.source: Retrieving the value of this property is an O(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 擷取這個屬性的值是一種 O(1) 運算。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through a collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回逐一查看集合的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" /> that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator`1" />，可用於逐一查看集合。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of the enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + +`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 會隱藏列舉值的複雜度。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 此位置<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>未定義屬性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，您必須呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法，以將列舉值前進到第一個項目，再讀取的值集合的<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> property returns the same object until <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>屬性會傳回相同的物件直到<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>呼叫。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: You cannot set <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again; you must create a new enumerator instance instead.
trans-unit.target: 您不能再次將 <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個項目；您必須建立新的列舉值執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果對集合進行變更，例如加入、修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，且其行為未定義。

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread-safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式沒有集合的獨佔存取權，因此，列舉集合內容本質上並不是安全的執行緒程序。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through a collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回逐一查看集合的列舉值。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" />，可用於逐一查看集合。

trans-unit.source: The `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in C++, `For Each` in Visual Basic) hides the complexity of the enumerators.
trans-unit.target: `foreach` C# 語言的陳述式 (`for each` c + +`For Each`在 Visual Basic 中) 會隱藏列舉值的複雜度。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, using `foreach` is recommended, instead of directly manipulating the enumerator.
trans-unit.target: 因此，建議您使用 `foreach`，而不要直接使用列舉值。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators can be used to read the data in the collection, but they cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 列舉程式可以用來讀取集合中的資料，但是無法用來修改基礎集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 一開始，列舉程式位在集合中的第一個項目之前。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> also brings the enumerator back to this position.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> 也會將列舉值帶回至這個位置。

trans-unit.source: At this position, the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 此位置<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>未定義屬性。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，您必須呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法，以將列舉值前進到第一個項目，再讀取的值集合的<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> property returns the same object until either <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>屬性會傳回相同的物件直到<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>或<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A>呼叫。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> sets <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> to the next element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> 會將 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 設定為下一個項目。

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> passes the end of the collection, the enumerator is positioned after the last element in the collection and <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>超過集合的列舉值的結尾會位於集合中的最後一個元素之後和<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the enumerator is at this position, subsequent calls to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> also return `false`.
trans-unit.target: 列舉值位於這個位置上，後續呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>也會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: If the last call to <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果最後一個呼叫<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>傳回`false`，<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A>是未定義。

trans-unit.source: To set <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> to the first element of the collection again, you can call <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> followed by <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 若要再次將 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A> 設定為集合的第一個元素，您可以在呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A> 之後，接著呼叫 <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A>。

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 只要集合維持不變，列舉程式就持續有效。

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: 如果對集合進行變更，例如加入、修改或刪除項目，列舉程式會永久失效，且其行為未定義。

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> has a fixed size.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，指出 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> 是否有固定的大小。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> has a fixed size; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see langword="true" /> 有固定大小，則為 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: In the default implementation of <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, this property always returns <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的預設實作中，這個屬性一律會傳回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: A collection with a fixed size does not allow the addition or removal of elements after the collection is created, but it allows the modification of existing elements.
trans-unit.target: 具有固定大小的集合不允許在集合建立後新增或移除項目，但允許對現有項目進行修改。

trans-unit.source: A collection with a fixed size is simply a collection with a wrapper that prevents adding and removing elements; therefore, if changes are made to the underlying collection, including the addition or removal of elements, the fixed-size collection reflects those changes.
trans-unit.target: 具有固定大小的集合是唯讀的集合只以防止新增或移除項目; 包裝函式因此，如果變更基礎的集合，包括新增或移除項目，固定大小的集合會反映這些變更。

trans-unit.target: 取得值，指出 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> 是否唯讀。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" /> is read-only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see langword="true" /> 是唯讀，則為 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IList" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.target: 在 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 的預設實作中，這個屬性一律會傳回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: A collection that is read-only does not allow the addition, removal, or modification of elements after the collection is created.
trans-unit.target: 唯讀的集合不允許在集合建立後增加、移除或修改項目。

trans-unit.source: A collection that is read-only is simply a collection with a wrapper that prevents modifying the collection; therefore, if changes are made to the underlying collection, the read-only collection reflects those changes.
trans-unit.target: 是唯讀的集合是唯讀的集合只具有可防止修改集合的包裝函式因此，如果基礎集合進行變更，唯讀的集合會反映這些變更。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.ToArray%2A> method and other methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class that act on ranges.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.ToArray%2A>以及的其他方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>處理範圍的類別。

trans-unit.source: At the end of the example, the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.GetRange%2A> method is used to get three items from the list, beginning with index location 2.
trans-unit.target: 在此範例中，結尾<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.GetRange%2A>方法用來取得從清單中，從索引位置 2 的三個項目。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.ToArray%2A> method is called on the resulting <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>, creating an array of three elements.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.ToArray%2A>方法會呼叫產生<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>，建立三個元素的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the array are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 陣列的項目會顯示。

trans-unit.source: Sets the capacity to the actual number of elements in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" />, if that number is less than a threshold value.
trans-unit.target: 將容量設為 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中項目的實際數目，如果該數目小於臨界值。

trans-unit.source: This method can be used to minimize a collection's memory overhead if no new elements will be added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法可用記憶體降到最低集合的額外負荷如果沒有新的項目會加入至集合。

trans-unit.source: The cost of reallocating and copying a large <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> can be considerable, however, so the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method does nothing if the list is at more than 90 percent of capacity.
trans-unit.target: 重新配置及複製大型的成本<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>相當大，但是，可能會因此<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法沒有作用，如果清單是在超過容量的 90%。

trans-unit.source: This avoids incurring a large reallocation cost for a relatively small gain.
trans-unit.target: 這可避免產生大型重新配置成本相對較小的改善。

trans-unit.source: The current threshold of 90 percent might change in future releases.
trans-unit.target: 90%的目前閾值可能在未來版本中變更。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: To reset a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> to its initial state, call the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A> method before calling the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要重設<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>設為初始狀態，請呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Clear%2A>方法之前先呼叫<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: Trimming an empty <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> sets the capacity of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> to the default capacity.
trans-unit.target: 修剪空白<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>設定的容量<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>預設容量。

trans-unit.source: The capacity can also be set using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 容量也可以設定使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>屬性。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to check the capacity and count of a <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> that contains a simple business object, and illustrates using the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method to remove extra capacity.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何檢查的容量和計數<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>的包含簡單商務物件，並說明如何使用<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法，以移除額外的容量。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: Several properties and methods of the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> class are used to add, insert, and remove items from a list of strings.
trans-unit.target: 數個屬性和方法<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>類別可用來加入、 插入和移除項目從字串的清單。

trans-unit.source: Then the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A> method is used to reduce the capacity to match the count, and the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A> and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A> properties are displayed.
trans-unit.target: 然後在<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrimExcess%2A>方法用來減少的容量，以符合計數，而<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Capacity%2A>和<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>屬性會顯示。

trans-unit.source: If the unused capacity had been less than 10 percent of total capacity, the list would not have been resized.
trans-unit.target: 如果未使用的容量已低於 10%的總容量，清單就不調整大小。

trans-unit.source: Finally, the contents of the list are cleared.
trans-unit.target: 最後，會清除清單的內容。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> delegate that defines the conditions to check against the elements.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Predicate`1" /> 委派，可定義檢查項目所根據的條件。

trans-unit.source: Determines whether every element in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> matches the conditions defined by the specified predicate.
trans-unit.target: 判斷 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的每一個項目是否符合指定之述詞所定義的條件。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if every element in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> matches the conditions defined by the specified predicate; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.List`1" /> 中的每一個項目都符合指定之述詞所定義的條件，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: If the list has no elements, the return value is <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果清單中沒有項目，則傳回值為 <see langword="true" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Predicate%601> is a delegate to a method that returns `true` if the object passed to it matches the conditions defined in the delegate.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Predicate%601>委派的方法會傳回以`true`傳送至的物件是否符合在委派中定義的條件。

trans-unit.source: The elements of the current <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> are individually passed to the <xref:System.Predicate%601> delegate, and processing is stopped when the delegate returns `false` for any element.
trans-unit.target: 目前的項目<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>分別傳遞至<xref:System.Predicate%601>的委派，以及處理在委派傳回時停止`false`的任何項目。

trans-unit.source: The elements are processed in order, and all calls are made on a single thread.
trans-unit.target: 依順序處理項目，且所有呼叫都都會在單一執行緒上。

trans-unit.source: This method is an O(*n*) operation, where *n* is <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法是 O (*n*) 作業，其中*n*是<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrueForAll%2A> method and several other methods that use <xref:System.Predicate%601> generic delegate.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrueForAll%2A>以及數個使用其他方法<xref:System.Predicate%601>泛型委派。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601> of strings is created, containing 8 dinosaur names, two of which (at positions 1 and 5) end with "saurus".
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601>字串的建立，其中包含 8 恐龍名稱，兩個 （在位置 1 和 5） 」 saurus 」 以結束。

trans-unit.source: The example also defines a search predicate method named `EndsWithSaurus`, which accepts a string parameter and returns a Boolean value indicating whether the input string ends in "saurus".
trans-unit.target: 此範例也會定義名為的搜尋述詞方法`EndsWithSaurus`、 可接受字串參數和傳回布林值，指出是否"saurus"輸入的字串結尾。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrueForAll%2A> method traverses the list from the beginning, passing each element in turn to the `EndsWithSaurus` method.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Generic.List%601.TrueForAll%2A>方法周遊清單開頭，接著為傳遞每個項目從`EndsWithSaurus`方法。

trans-unit.source: The search stops when the `EndsWithSaurus` method returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: 搜尋會停止時`EndsWithSaurus`方法會傳回`false`。

trans-unit.source: In C# and Visual Basic, it is not necessary to create the `Predicate<string>` delegate (`Predicate(Of String)` in Visual Basic) explicitly.
trans-unit.target: 在 C# 和 Visual Basic 中，就不需要建立`Predicate<string>`委派 (`Predicate(Of String)`在 Visual Basic 中) 明確。

trans-unit.source: These languages infer the correct delegate from context and create it automatically.
trans-unit.target: 這些語言推斷正確的委派，從內容，並自動建立。
